steps.name: Given  Admin is logged into the LMS portal and on the dashboard page
When  Admin clicks the Delete icon for any batch
Then  Admin should see the confirm alert box with yes and no button
When  Admin clicks the "yes" button on the confirm alert box
Then  Admin should see a successful message and the batch should be deleted
